item.title: Trump to deploy National Guard in response to Los Angeles immigration protests
item.description: California Gov. Gavin Newsom said that Trump was being "purposefully inflammatory" in sending National Guard troops to L.A.

item.title: Trump says Elon Musk will face 'serious consequences' if he backs Democratic candidates
item.description: President Donald Trump also said that he thinks his relationship with Elon Musk is done after their public feud erupted this week.

item.title: Vance says Musk making a 'huge mistake' in going after Trump but also tries to downplay the attacks
item.description: Vice President JD Vance said Elon Musk was making a "huge mistake" going after President Donald Trump after a falling out between the two men.

item.title: Protesters rally against ICE for second day in Los Angeles
item.description: Federal agents in Los Angeles faced off against demonstrators protesting immigration raids following Friday's protests.

item.title: Elon Musk appears to delete some explosive X posts amid feud with Trump
item.description: It's the latest twist in the public spat between Elon Musk and President Donald Trump that escalated this week.
